author: brane
msg: On the authzperf branch: Simplify the constructor semantics, since the authz
parser will not need all the extra bells and whistles. We can still add them
at a later date if we happen to actually need them.
ci_section_names, ci_option_names, defaults, options and order.
(open_section, close_section, add_value): Make these simple wrappers
around the constructor callbacks, and handle loop termination.
(svn_config__parse_stream): Update calls to open_section and close_section.
